时代》杂志将其评为20世纪最优秀的电视剧作[5]；2000年1月14日，《辛普森一家》的星星被刻在了好莱坞星光大道上。作为美国历史上最长寿的情景喜剧[6]及动画节目[7]，《辛普森一家》对流行文化产生了极大的影响：譬如霍默·辛普森懊恼时的咕哝声“D'oh!”便被英语词典所收录；同时此剧亦对许多面向成人的动画情景喜剧产生了影响。","name":"The Simpsons Season 1","name_cn":"辛普森一家 第一季","tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":76,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":64,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"辛普森","count":24,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1989","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Simpsons","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美动画","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国民动画","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国动画","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美漫","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MattGroening","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"辛普森一家","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1989年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980-1989","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"杂","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"级数太多","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"无","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"THE","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补旧番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"讽刺","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"坑","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"DanCastellaneta","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"20thTelevision","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"T4","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"辛普森一家 第一季"},{"key":"话数","value":"13"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"1989年12月17日"},{"key":"放送星期","value":"星期日"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"CBS"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"1990年5月13日"}],"rating":{"rank":1064,"total":234,"count":{"1":2,"2":0,"3":1,"4":0,"5":5,"6":28,"7":73,"8":88,"9":27,"10":10},"score":7.5},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":41,"dropped":31,"wish":205,"collect":397,"doing":60},"id":19889,"eps":13,"meta_tags":["TV","美国","欧美"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,